<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../partials/new-head', { title: 'Press Kit — Kidamame' , url: 'https://www.kidamame.com/press-kit.html' })
    %>

    <body>
        <%- include('../partials/new-nav', { alwaysScrolled: true, hideNavItems: false }) %>

            <!-- LEGAL CONTENT / PRESS KIT -->
            <section class="legal-content">
                <div class="legal-container reveal">
                    <h1>Press Kit</h1>

                    <p>Welcome to the Kidamame Press Kit. Here you can find high-resolution logos, screenshots, and
                        brand assets for media, press, and promotional use.</p>

                    <h2>Brand Logos</h2>
                    <p>Download our official logos suitable for both light and dark
                        backgrounds.</p>
                    <a href="downloads/kidamame-logos.zip" class="btn-primary"
                        style="display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 2rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i>
                        Download Logos (ZIP)</a>

                    <h2>App Screenshots & Artworks</h2>
                    <p>High-resolution screenshots from <strong>Kidamame Discovery</strong> showcasing the environments,
                        animals, and "Did You Know?" fact cards.</p>
                    <a href="downloads/kidamame-screenshots.zip" class="btn-primary"
                        style="display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 2rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i>
                        Download Photos (ZIP)</a>

                    <h2>Guidelines</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Please do not alter the colors, aspect ratio, or shape of our logos.</li>
                        <li>Give appropriate breathing room around our logos.</li>
                        <li>If you need specific formats or sizes not included here, please reach out to us.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>Contact for Press</h2>
                    <p>If you're writing an article, need an interview, or have other press inquiries, please contact us
                        directly at <a href="mailto:info@kidamame.com"
                            style="color: var(--blue); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">info@kidamame.com</a>.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <%- include('../partials/new-footer') %>
